vsParam:
Guys, I have something about Netl to tell you.
Do you have time?

Um, of course, Angelica.
What is it?

I want to make peace with Netl.
After all... He's my only little brother.

But I'm no good with words,
so I'm thinking about giving him a gift.

Oh, a gift! That's a good idea.
What do you have in mind?

Er... an amulet commonly seen in my hometown.
My parents... taught me how to make it.

We'd pray for our loved ones to be safe and sound
when we make it... so it's a lucky amulet.

Wonderful!
That's the best gift to give when you seek a reconciliation!

Yes. So,
I hope that [px] can help me make the amulet.

Sure, no problem...
What's it made of?

Simply linking up mineral ornaments with a specially-made
string will make a beautiful amulet.

I'll make the string...
I want to ask [px] to make the mineral ornaments.

I believe that [px] will devote all [px]'s love to this amulet
just like me...

[px], Angelica.
With this amulet of love, he will...

Netl will open his heart!
Ah, but... we also want to help!

Er, yes!
Let Netl also feel our love for him!

OK, so, let's all work together to help
Netl and Angelica reconcile!
